lines.text: Re: MARYAM KAMANDI Nov 13, 1935 Age: 89 yr HN: 8188 240
Amlodipine 5 mg 1 time daily for 3 months of 30 days dose increased
to 10 mg temporary by nephrologist, please give her 10 mg for one
gabapentin 100 mg every day at bedtime for 90 days
Crestor 5 mg other for 3 months of 30 days Q other day
Tecta 40 mg 1 tablet 1 time daily, PRN for 45 days
isosorbide dinitrate 10 mg 2 times daily for 90 days
Thank you again for seeing this patient. I look forward to hearing back
